<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Floral Dreamland</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-image: url('Pink-Flower-Best-Wallpaper-43967.jpg'); /* Background */
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      color: #fff;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px #000;
    }
    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 38px;
      color: #ffddee;
    }
    .gallery {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-around;
      margin-top: 50px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .gallery img {
      width: 300px;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 20px;
      margin: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }
    .poem {
      margin: 60px auto;
      width: 80%;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h1>“Step into a dreamy wonderland where butterflies whisper secrets, flowers glow with joy, and magic blooms in every petal! ✨🦋🌸💖🌷💫🌼🍃🌺🌈🌟🌹🎀🧚‍♀️”</h1>

  <div class="gallery">
    <img src="125c0c9a0fed2e9f3bb03305c4b3ed64.jpg" alt="Elegant roses">
    <img src="depositphotos_64909923-stock-photo-beautiful-flowers-background.jpg" alt="Colorful garden">
    <img src="azalea-1508785048.jpg" alt="Pink blossoms">
  </div>

  <div class="poem">
    🌸 In the garden of dreams, where petals fall like rain, <br>
    Every flower whispers love, soft and pure, without pain. 💖🌷<br><br>

    🦋 Butterflies dance like joy set free, <br>
    In a world made of colors and fantasy. 🌈🌼<br><br>

    🌺 The roses blush in morning light, <br>
    Spreading fragrance and sheer delight. 🌹✨<br><br>

    💫 With every bloom, a story grows, <br>
    Of silent winds and how beauty flows. 🍃🧚‍♀️<br><br>

    🌷 Let your heart bloom, just like this field, <br>
    Where every emotion is softly revealed. 🎀🌸<br><br>

    🌟 Welcome, dear soul, to this floral spell, <br>
    Where magic and peace forever dwell. 🌼🌷🌟<br>
  </div>

</body>
<div class="poem">
  🦋 In a land beyond clouds, where time melts away,<br>
  Butterflies sing softly, guiding dreams that stray. 💭🌸<br><br>

  🌷 Flowers bloom with gentle pride,<br>
  As morning dew clings to their side. 💧🌼<br><br>

  🧚‍♀️ Fairies hum in golden beams,<br>
  Telling tales of love in moonlit dreams. 🌙✨<br><br>

  🌹 Roses speak with velvet sighs,<br>
  While petals float like lullabies. 🎶🌺<br><br>

  🦋 Wings of blue, wings of flame,<br>
  Each one carries a secret name. 📜💫<br><br>

  🌈 Rainbows curl around the breeze,<br>
  And butterflies dance between the trees. 🌳🌟<br><br>

  🍃 The leaves applaud with every gust,<br>
  In a garden built on hope and trust. ❤️🌼<br><br>

  💐 Tulips laugh in shades of spring,<br>
  As bees and birds together sing. 🎵🐦🐝<br><br>

  🧡 The daisies sway in golden light,<br>
  Holding sunshine through the night. 🌞🌕<br><br>

  🌻 Even the silence here is sweet,<br>
  Beneath each flower, a heartbeat. 💓🌸<br><br>

  🦋 Whispering wings brush your skin,<br>
  Awakening love that lives within. 💖✨<br><br>

  🌺 So close your eyes, and just believe,<br>
  The garden’s magic will never leave. 🌌🌼<br><br>

  🌟 You’re not just walking in the flowers —<br>
  You’re walking through your soul’s own powers. 🦋🌸💫<br><br>

  🎀 Let go of pain, let peace unfold,<br>
  In this butterfly world of dreams untold. 🌈🌷💖<br><br>

  🦋 Welcome home, where the heart can sing,<br>
  With every flower… and every wing. 🌹🧚‍♀️✨
</div>
</body>
</HTML>
